  "detailed_description": "<h1>About This Game</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616210/extras/7c00f4f4249d456c083c58faf73593d4.poster.avif?t=1747836472\" width=800 height=800 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616210/extras/7c00f4f4249d456c083c58faf73593d4.webm?t=1747836472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616210/extras/7c00f4f4249d456c083c58faf73593d4.mp4?t=1747836472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>In the game you have to go through obstacles, overcome moving platforms, during the game you will encounter difficult obstacles to go further, important in this game will be to have a lot of patience, the way to best complete the game will not always have to <i><strong>jump</strong></i> but get on the moving platform as quickly as <strong>possible</strong>.</p></p><br><h1>About This Game</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Sometimes you don't have to jump, but quickly get onto a moving platform</i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616210/extras/833ba9e70bf7d858f3e1b64d04a6f394.poster.avif?t=1747836472\" width=800 height=800 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616210/extras/833ba9e70bf7d858f3e1b64d04a6f394.webm?t=1747836472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616210/extras/833ba9e70bf7d858f3e1b64d04a6f394.mp4?t=1747836472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616210/extras/7926dc1e3d5736669ee8aae1d13e6b74.avif?t=1747836472\" width=800 height=374 /></span>\"Jump\" is an arcade game based on the parkour theme. You need great skills to complete it in its entirety. You start with easy obstacles and as you progress, you move on to more and more difficult ones. The controls consist of pointing the character in the right direction and pressing the JUMP button at the right moment. It's not as easy as you think... Test your skills and try to complete challenging stages that will certainly cause you a lot of difficulties.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616210/extras/7926dc1e3d5736669ee8aae1d13e6b74.avif?t=1747836472\" width=800 height=374 /></span>\"Jump\" is an arcade game based on the parkour theme. You need great skills to complete it in its entirety. You start with easy obstacles and as you progress, you move on to more and more difficult ones. The controls consist of pointing the character in the right direction and pressing the JUMP button at the right moment. It's not as easy as you think... Test your skills and try to complete challenging stages that will certainly cause you a lot of difficulties.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
